code: import axios from"axios";const API_BASE_URL="/api";export const getNearestOffices=async(latitude,longitude,jwtToken)=>{try{const response=await axios.get("".concat(API_BASE_URL,"/offices?lat=").concat(latitude,"&lng=").concat(longitude),{headers:{Authorization:"Bearer ".concat(jwtToken)}});return response.data;}catch(error){console.error("Error fetching nearest offices:",error);return[];}};
